long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Naughty Rubber Duck is a tool that uses chaotic methods to encourage you to finish your work… or else.

With 3 different settings, and a variety of playful text-to-speech catchphrases, 
you’ll accomplish your work faster than ever.

A Same Day Skunkworks project - Made with <3 by Agency Enterprise
